Short message application

Environment
Ubuntu 11.10
Rails 3.1.1
ruby 1.9.3p6 (2011-12-20 revision 34080) [i686-linux] (This will have Chinese problem and need magic_encoding which can solve it)
or 
ruby 1.8.7 (2011-02-18 patchlevel 334) [i686-linux]
gem version 1.8.11
Bundler version 1.0.21

Installation
bundle install
rake db:migrate
